351
00:24:31,460 --> 00:24:33,395
Your name?

352
00:24:33,395 --> 00:24:35,197
Misato Urano.

353
00:24:35,197 --> 00:24:37,432
You find her unforgivable?

354
00:24:37,432 --> 00:24:41,536
She thinks nothing of human life.

355
00:24:41,536 --> 00:24:43,705
To her, this world is
about prestige and glory.

356
00:24:43,705 --> 00:24:46,808
She said life is ultimately just a game.

357
00:24:46,808 --> 00:24:48,977
Your wish?

358
00:24:48,977 --> 00:24:52,080
Banish her to Hell for me!

